name: My First Songs 2
description:
My First Songs 2 is the best interactive music game for kids, with a playlist of 14 popular children’s songs, charming 3D animations, and lots of cute characters and animals!

Sing along and pop bubble notes: try to catch them all!

Playlist:

- Head Shoulders Knees and Toes

- Deck the Hall

- Ten Little Indians

- Hey Diddle Diddle

- Humpty Dumpty

- If You’re Happy and You Know It

- Little Miss Muffet

- Pop Goes the Weasel

- Row, Row, Row Your Boat

- The Muffin Man

- The Wheel on the Bus

- We Wish You A Merry Christmas

- Little Bo Peep

- Oh Where Has My Little Dog Gone
